<!DOCTYPE html>
<html>
<head>
  <meta http-equiv="Content-Type" content="text/html; charset=utf-8">
  <style>
    body { font-family: sans-serif; color: #222; background: #f9f9f9; margin: 0; padding: 0; }
    .container { max-width: 560px; margin: 40px auto; background: #fff; border-radius: 8px; padding: 40px; }
    .btn { display: inline-block; background: #1a1a2e; color: #fff; padding: 14px 28px; border-radius: 6px; text-decoration: none; font-weight: bold; margin-top: 24px; }
    .footer { margin-top: 32px; font-size: 13px; color: #888; }
  </style>
</head>
<body>
  <div class="container">
    <h2>You've been invited to Revnous</h2>
    <p><strong><%= @inviter_name %></strong> has invited you to join Revnous as an admin.</p>
    <p>Click the button below to accept or decline the invitation. This link expires in <strong>72 hours</strong> (<%= @expires_at.strftime("%B %d, %Y at %H:%M %Z") %>).</p>

    <a href="<%= @accept_url %>" class="btn">View Invitation</a>

    <div class="footer">
      <p>If you weren't expecting this invitation, you can safely ignore this email.</p>
      <p>Or copy this link: <%= @accept_url %></p>
    </div>
  </div>
</body>
</html>
